title: Person trapped in truck after Lithgow bridge collapse
description: A person is trapped after a bridge collapsed onto a truck in Lithgow, NSW. The cherry picker crashed into a rail bridge on Inch Rd about 9am on Thursday.   Emergency services remain at the scene and are continuing to free the man. The rail bridge is currently not in operation but drivers are being urged to avoid the area.  #truckcrash #railbridge #crash #trap #Lithgow #NSW
